WAFER WORKS OPTR said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 75.83% to NT$17,063,000 from NT$70,588,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             17,063           70,588    
YOY%             -75.83%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales             48,431          250,944    
YOY%             -80.70% 
=================================================================
 